Produce Flame

With this spell, the druid can conjure into existence
a small globe of pure elemental flame.  The flame will
serve as a light source, and can also be commanded to
burn an enemy for a small amount of damage, although
doing this will reduce the flame's lifespan.

Command: produce
Base Cost: 35 SP plus 10 SP per 'burn'
Base Recovery: medium
Base Effect: light, damage (low)
Base Duration: very long
Guild Level: 2
